<p class="c13"><span class="c2">B&ecirc;n A giao cho b&ecirc;n B ti&#7871;n h&agrave;nh &#273;o v&#7869; c&#259;n nh&agrave; s&#7889;: </span> <strong>{{$design->home_add}}</strong>, <span class="c2">&#272;&#432;&#7901;ng <strong>{{$design->street}}</strong> Ph&#432;&#7901;ng <strong>{{$design->ward}}</strong> Qu&#7853;n <strong>{{$design->district}}</strong> do &Ocirc;ng (B&agrave;): <strong>&nbsp;{{$design->customer}}</strong> l&agrave; ch&#7911; s&#7903; h&#7919;u. Theo m&#7851;u b&#7843;n v&#7869; do V&#259;n Ph&ograve;ng &#272;&#259;ng K&yacute; &#272;&#7845;t &#272;ai Chi Nh&aacute;nh Qu&#7853;n T&acirc;n B&igrave;nh qui &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; k&yacute; ki&#7875;m n&#7897;i nghi&#7879;p.</span></p>
<p class="c5"><span class="c2"></span></p><p class="c17 c20"><span class="c0">&#272;i&#7873;u 2: TR&Aacute;CH NHI&#7878;M HAI B&Ecirc;N</span></p>
  <li class="c6"><span class="c19 c0">B&ecirc;n A:<br>
  </span><span class="c2">- C&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m cung c&#7845;p c&aacute;c gi&#7845;y t&#7901; c&oacute; li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n c&#259;n nh&agrave; c&#7847;n &#273;o v&#7869;.<br>
  </span><span class="c2">- H&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n v&agrave; ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n v&#7873; ranh nh&agrave; v&agrave; &#273;&#7845;t.<br>
  </span><span class="c2">- T&#7841;o &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i cho b&ecirc;n B ti&#7871;n h&agrave;nh kh&#7843;o s&aacute;t &#273;o v&#7869; nh&agrave; &#273;&#7845;t.</span></li>
  <li class="c6"><span class="c19 c0">B&ecirc;n B:<br>
  </span><span class="c2">- C&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m &#273;o v&#7869; &#273;&uacute;ng hi&#7879;n tr&#7841;ng th&#7921;c t&#7871;, giao cho b&ecirc;n A 05 b&#7843;n v&#7869;.<br>
      - 
  </span><span class="c2">Thay m&#7863;t b&ecirc;n A th&ocirc;ng qua ph&#7847;n ki&#7875;m tra n&#7897;i nghi&#7879;p c&#7911;a Chi Nh&aacute;nh &nbsp;V&#259;n Ph&ograve;ng &#272;o &#272;&#7841;c &#272;&#7845;t &#272;ai Qu&#7853;n T&acirc;n &nbsp;B&igrave;nh. </span></li>
  </ol><p class="c3"><span class="c2"></span></p><p class="c17 c20"><span class="c0">&#272;i&#7873;u 3: GI&Aacute; TR&#7882; H&#7906;P &#272;&#7890;NG</span></p><p class="c14"><span class="c2">Chi ph&iacute; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n b&#7843;n v&#7869; (bao g&#7891;m chi ph&iacute; &nbsp;&#273;o v&#7869; &#273;&#7883;a ch&iacute;nh, x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh t&#7885;a &#273;&#7897; v&#7883; &nbsp;tr&iacute; &#273;&#7845;t v&agrave; chi ph&iacute; &#273;o v&#7869; hi&#7879;n tr&#7841;ng nh&agrave;) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh theo &#273;&#417;n gi&aacute; sau:<br>
  </span><span class="c2">- Di&#7879;n t&iacute;ch s&agrave;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng, ban c&ocirc;ng : {{$design->area_s}}/m2<br>
  </span><span class="c2">- Di&#7879;n t&iacute;ch s&acirc;n th&#432;&#7907;ng, hi&ecirc;n : {{$design->area_sth}}/m2<br>
  </span><span class="c2">- Di&#7879;n t&iacute;ch s&acirc;n tr&#7889;ng, &#273;&#7845;t tr&#7889;ng (&#273;&#7871;n 1.000m2): {{$design->area_stsd}}/m2</span></p>
  <p class="c14"><span class="c2">* Gi&aacute; tr&#7883; t&#7889;i thi&#7875;u m&#7897;t b&#7843;n v&#7869; HT nh&agrave; &ndash; &#273;&#7845;t &nbsp;l&agrave; {{number_format($design->min_cost,0,",",".")}}&#273; /c&#259;n. </span></p>
<p class="c7"><span class="c2"></span></p><p class="c17 c20"><span class="c0">&#272;i&#7873;u 4: TH&#7874; TH&#7912;C THANH TO&Aacute;N: </span></p><p class="c17 c20"><span class="c9">Thanh to&aacute;n b&#7857;ng ti&#7873;n m&#7863;t v&agrave; chia l&agrave;m hai l&#7847;n</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">- L&#7847;n 1: Sau khi k&yacute; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng, b&ecirc;n A t&#7841;m &#7913;ng {{number_format($design->received_cost,0,",",".") }}&#273;/c&#259;n nh&agrave;.</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">- L&#7847;n 2: Sau khi nh&#7853;n b&#7843;n v&#7869;, b&ecirc;n A &nbsp;s&#7869; thanh to&aacute;n ph&#7847;n c&ograve;n l&#7841;i.</span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c2"></span></p><p class="c17 c20"><span class="c0">&#272;i&#7873;u 5: &#272;I&#7872;U KHO&#7842;N THI H&Agrave;NH</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">Ti&#7873;n t&#7841;m &#7913;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ho&agrave;n l&#7841;i trong c&aacute;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p sau:</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">- B&ecirc;n A b&aacute;o h&#7911;y h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c khi nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n B &#273;&#7871;n kh&#7843;o s&aacute;t th&#7921;c t&#7871;, ho&agrave;n tr&#7843; 100%</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">- Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p &#273;&atilde; kh&#7843;o s&aacute;t : &nbsp;ho&agrave;n tr&#7843; 70%</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">- Khi &#273;&atilde; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n vi&#7879;c &#273;o v&agrave; l&#7853;p b&#7843;n v&#7869; c&ocirc;ng ty kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t ho&agrave;n tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n l&#7841;i n&#7919;a.</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">H&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7853;p th&agrave;nh 02 b&#7843;n, m&#7895;i b&ecirc;n gi&#7919; 01 b&#7843;n, c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; nh&#432; nhau:</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">Th&#7901;i gian kh&#7843;o s&aacute;t nh&agrave;: {{$design->time}} ngày .S&#7889; &#272;T li&ecirc;n h&#7879;: (08) 22 478 959</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">Th&#7901;i gian tr&#7843; b&#7843;n v&#7869; ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o th&#7901;i gian x&aacute;c minh v&agrave; k&yacute; ki&#7875;m c&#7911;a V&#259;n Ph&ograve;ng &#272;&#259;ng K&yacute; &#272;&#7845;t &#272;ai Chi Nh&aacute;nh Qu&#7853;n T&acirc;n B&igrave;nh.</span></p>
<p class="c15"><span class="c2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p class="c17 c20"><span class="c0">&#272;i&#7873;u 6: &#272;I&#7872;U KHO&#7842;N THANH L&Yacute; H&#7906;P &#272;&#7890;NG</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">- H&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng coi nh&#432; &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thanh l&yacute; sau khi b&ecirc;n A &nbsp;nh&#7853;n &nbsp;&#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7843;n v&#7869;.</span></p>
<p class="c17 c20"><span class="c2">- H&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng ch&#7881; c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; trong v&ograve;ng 8 th&aacute;ng (k&#7875; t&#7915; ng&agrave;y k&yacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng), sau th&#7901;i gian tr&ecirc;n xem nh&#432; &nbsp;do b&ecirc;n A &#273;&atilde; t&#7921; &yacute; h&#7911;y b&#7887;. </span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c2"></span></p>
